@startuml SD-08_Notifications

skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam defaultFontName "Arial"
skinparam defaultFontSize 17
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam dpi 300

skinparam participant {
    BackgroundColor #FFFFFF
    BorderColor #555555
    BorderThickness 1
    FontColor #000000
    FontStyle plain
}
skinparam actor {
    BackgroundColor #FFFFFF
    BorderColor #555555
    BorderThickness 1
    FontColor #000000
}
skinparam sequence {
    ArrowColor #333333
    ArrowThickness 1
    ArrowFontColor #000000
    ArrowFontSize 16
    LifeLineBorderColor #333333
    LifeLineBorderThickness 1
    LifeLineBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
    GroupBodyBackgroundColor #F8F8F8
    GroupBorderColor #888888
    GroupBorderThickness 1
    GroupHeaderFontColor #000000
    DividerBackgroundColor #E8E8E8
    DividerFontColor #000000
    DividerBorderColor #AAAAAA
    DividerBorderThickness 1
    ParticipantBorderThickness 1
}
skinparam note {
    BackgroundColor #FAFAFA
    BorderColor #999999
    BorderThickness 1
    FontColor #000000
}

actor       "User"         as User
participant "Web\nUI"      as UI
participant "Notif.\nController" as Ctrl
participant "Notif.\nService"    as Svc
participant "Event\nSystem"      as Events
database    "DB"           as DB

' ═════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
== Creation (Event-Driven) ==
' ═════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

note over Events, DB
  [Planned] When scan/AI completes,
  an event listener creates a
  Notification record in DB.
end note

Events -> Svc  : on("scan.completed")
Svc  -> DB  : save(Notification { type: SCAN })
DB  --> Svc  : saved

Events -> Svc  : on("ai.analysis.completed")
Svc  -> DB  : save(Notification { type: AI })
DB  --> Svc  : saved

' ═════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
== Fetch Notifications ==
' ═════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

User -> UI   : Open panel
UI   -> Ctrl : GET /api/notifications
Ctrl -> Svc  : findAll()
Svc  -> DB  : find() order by date
DB  --> Svc  : notifications[]
Svc --> Ctrl : notifications[]
Ctrl --> UI  : 200 OK
UI  --> User : Show list & badge

' ═══════════════════════════════════════════
== Mark Single as Read ==
' ═══════════════════════════════════════════

User -> UI   : Click notification
UI   -> Ctrl : PATCH /.../:id/read
Ctrl -> Svc  : markAsRead(id)
Svc  -> DB  : save({ isRead: true })
DB  --> Svc  : updated
Svc --> Ctrl : notification
Ctrl --> UI  : 200 OK
UI  --> User : Item marked read

' ═════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
== Mark All as Read ==
' ═════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

User -> UI   : Click "Mark all as read"
UI   -> Ctrl : PATCH /.../read-all
Ctrl -> Svc  : markAllAsRead()
Svc  -> DB  : update(isRead = true)
DB  --> Svc  : rows affected
Svc --> Ctrl : { success: true }
Ctrl --> UI  : 200 OK
UI  --> User : Badge cleared

@enduml
